    "title": "Directorate &amp; Operations Support Supervisor",
    "excerpt": "<p>As the Directorate and Operations Support Supervisor (Supervisor II), you will work directly with executive leadership to advance ODI’s priorities. Acting as a central operational gatekeeper, you will lead a dedicated administrative team, manage high-visibility initiatives, and provide strategic policy, fiscal, and operational support to the Director and Chief Deputy Director. Location: The employee’s workstation &#8230; <a title=\"Directorate &amp; Operations Support Supervisor\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/join-us/directorate-operations-support-supervisor/\" aria-label=\"More on Directorate &amp; Operations Support Supervisor\">Read more</a></p>\n",
